36
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,360
Just give me a call if you need anything.

37
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,240
I'm leaving.

38
00:03:29,270 --> 00:03:30,079
I'm taking this with me.

39
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,550
