♫ The long awaited summer ♫

73
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:35,120
Do you remember?

74
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:38,240
Your childhood friends with
a complicated relationship?

75
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,960
♫ Is burning with heat ♫

76
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:39,940
